  <summary date="2021-04-20T16:05:56Z" status="Introduced in House">Pathway to Stable and Affordable Housing for All Act

This bill provides appropriations to the Department of Housing and Urban Development for several housing programs, including (1) Tenant-Based Rental Assistance, (2) the Housing Trust Fund, (3) the Continuum of Care Program, and (4) the Emergency Solutions Grants Program.</summary>
